">শব্দ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সম্পূর্ণভাবে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সমস্যমান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পদসমূহের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অনুগামী</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">না</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়ে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কোনো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিশিষ্ট</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অর্থ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গ্রহণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তাদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যোগরূঢ়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বলে</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">যেমন</span><span class=\"english\">: </span><span class=\"english\">পঙ্কজ</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">জলধি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ইত্যাদি</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর বণ্টন:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">অর্থগতভাবে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাংলা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তিনভাগে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভাগ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়েছে</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০</span><span class=\"english\">১</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">অর্থগতভাবে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাংলা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দের</span><span class=\"english\"> ৩ </span><span class=\"english\">টি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রকারভেদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নাম</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">অর্থগতভাবে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাংলা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">৩টি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রকারভেদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সংজ্ঞা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০</span><span class=\"english\">১</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সর্বমোট</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">০৩</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">বি.দ্র. প্রতি ২টি বানান ভুলের জন্য ০১ নম্বর করে কর্তন করা হবে।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">পরীক্ষক ভুলগুলো আন্ডারলাইন করে অবশ্যই ঠিক করে দিবেন।</span></p>"
